    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you my pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it\u2019s still in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new and ready for the road, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
