    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) powered by the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving unit features eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock. The mechanical integrity is absolute: rod bearings have been proactively replaced with VAC Motorsports coated bearings, and the throttle body actuators are recently serviced. The chassis remains factory-spec with a carbon-fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof to optimize the center of gravity. The Jerez Black Metallic finish exhibits original depth with no swirling, while the Novillo leather interior remains supple with zero bolster compression. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and a clean over-rev report.",
      "price": 46500.0,
